description:
Store sales of the in-game item TP Medals will end on May 15th 2024. 

*TP Medals already purchased will remain available in-game after the store sales end.
*STP Medals is scheduled to replace TP Medals at a later date.

Adds TP Medal (x500) to your inventory.
name: DRAGON BALL XENOVERSE 2 TP Medal (x500) #3
